<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Reliable. Gamer. Father. Mentor.</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile_image.jpg", width: 350, alt: "Profile Image", class: "profile-img" %>

        <div class="collapse skills" id="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-1">
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7">
        <p>Software engineer who loves experimenting, creating and reaching new limits with an innate desire to help, encourage and grow people. I thrive on contributing and making a difference in a world that is always in need of a little sunshine.</p>

        <p>I am passionately curious to learn and try new things to use my analytical skills, come up with intuitive solutions and solve complex problems. I come from a very fast-paced agile background where problems need immediate responses and clever solutions.</p>

        <p>My experience includes working solo and on teams, creating projects with deadlines, managing and developing teams to create the best experience with the highest quality for everyone. I work closely with project managers and my team to create great end results.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#skills"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="skills"
          >
            Skills
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jobs 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jobs 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
